00:15:09.640 --> 00:15:10.840
You still want to run?

00:15:11.160 --> 00:15:12.960
Where do you think you're going?

00:15:13.040 --> 00:15:13.900
Come back here!

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:18.080
Look at

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:19.540
what you've done to my son.

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:23.640
Ah!

00:15:23.640 --> 00:15:24.100
This...

00:15:24.400 --> 00:15:24.760
Oh my.

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:25.290
Oh my.

00:15:25.400 --> 00:15:25.840
Wait,

00:15:25.840 --> 00:15:26.700
where is my son?

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.440
Doctor! Nurse!